In fact, Many many years ago, Something terrible happened to me, as a direct consequence of my own actions. It changed me totally. I am much happier now than I was before this happened. But it was a mistake. I'm glad I made it now. <br>
It can be the little mistakes that change someones path enourmously. <br>
