<br>
There are all kinds. Vogue, Cosmo, and any of those other fashion magazines show us these painfully thin models conditioning our minds to think that thin is beautiful. <br>
<br>
What about that men have to be constantly strong and that if you show any kind of vulnerability that its considered a weakness? <br>
<br>
Society has these &quot;visions&quot; on how we &quot;should&quot; be and we push them on our children without even knowing it. <br>
<br>
Is there Social Brainwashing? Every damn day.  <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:purple;">Mysidia Drakkenbane</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
